# Open menu when clicking on desktop
Mouse 1 R A Menu FvwmRootMenu

DestroyMenu FvwmRootMenu
AddToMenu FvwmRootMenu
+ "Web Browser" Exec $[fvwm_webbrowser]
+ "Terminal Emulator" Exec $[fvwm_term]
+ "File Manager" Exec $[fvwm_filemanager]
+ "" Nop
+ "Change Wallpaper" Exec nitrogen
+ "Sound Settings" Exec pavucontrol
+ "" Nop
+ "FVWM Console" Module FvwmConsole
+ "Restart FVWM" Restart

DestroyMenu FvwmExitMenu
AddToMenu FvwmExitMenu "Exit" Title
+ "Log Off" Quit
+ "Restart" Exec systemctl reboot
+ "Suspend" Exec systemctl suspend
+ "Shut Down" Exec systemctl poweroff
